codeText: @Override_	protected Object resolveSpecifiedLookupKey(Object lookupKey) {_		if (lookupKey instanceof Integer) {_			return lookupKey__		}_		else if (lookupKey instanceof String) {_			String constantName = (String) lookupKey__			if (!constantName.startsWith(DefaultTransactionDefinition.PREFIX_ISOLATION)) {_				throw new IllegalArgumentException("Only isolation constants allowed")__			}_			return constants.asNumber(constantName)__		}_		else {_			throw new IllegalArgumentException(_					"Invalid lookup key - needs to be isolation level Integer or isolation level name String: " + lookupKey)__		}_	}
